{"pageProps":{"post":{"_createdAt":"2022-06-21T15:07:54Z","_id":"1335ed84-7b23-4ceb-a62b-332a57dfa6da","author":{"image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-339f8e320ddfad52225d31a181b162996e1c02d1-876x876-png","_type":"reference"}},"name":"ðŸ‘¾ Game Master"},"body":[{"_key":"9fb7a8aad2a2","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"8e6137e9a1920","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Before reading this article, it is highly recommended to have previous knowledge on "},{"_key":"8e6137e9a1921","_type":"span","marks":["99ccb72e3190"],"text":"Decentralization"},{"_key":"8e6137e9a1922","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" and "},{"_key":"8e6137e9a1923","_type":"span","marks":["a49333a926ef"],"text":"Decentralized Finance (De-Fi)"},{"_key":"8e6137e9a1924","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" so that readers can have a better understanding of the decentralized ecosystem."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"99ccb72e3190","_type":"link","href":"https://www.notion.so/Decentralization-8b55f0766a8a46b6a72fe22bbac59a42"},{"_key":"a49333a926ef","_type":"link","href":"https://www.notion.so/Decentralized-Finance-De-Fi-a904f1a54a2f48bdbb290ca639396150"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"b5376ac67dcf","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"6769eb6c09480","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"What is ICO"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h1"},{"_key":"ad10210e8f04","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"a4cb12f3fea50","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Initial coin offering, often called ICO, is a process in decentralized finance that resembles the "},{"_key":"a4cb12f3fea51","_type":"span","marks":["dddc6594b6a1"],"text":"Initial Public Offering (IPO)"},{"_key":"a4cb12f3fea52","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" process in traditional finance. ICO is a popular way decentralized companies choose to raise funds for future business operations."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"dddc6594b6a1","_type":"link","href":"https://www.notion.so/Initial-Public-Offering-IPO-48856ead20a646eabf690a02305b2f07"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"f95ac9454fdc","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"9dad13717d57","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"3a68a8a2ee8c","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-c329b1adb98b37bbff279be1b933ebb5f70a7da7-730x400-png","_type":"reference"}},{"_key":"4a14837922e2","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7b9017e7e9c30","_type":"span","marks":["em"],"text":"Image source: "},{"_key":"7b9017e7e9c31","_type":"span","marks":["2761c38b792a","em"],"text":"https://media.warriortrading.com/2018/01/Blog_ICO1.jpg"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"2761c38b792a","_type":"link","href":"https://media.warriortrading.com/2018/01/Blog_ICO1.jpg"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"a318bd0b03ea","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f9dda6a577f20","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"How Does ICO Work?"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h1"},{"_key":"ff758af4ab53","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"364708be87b60","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"During the process of ICO, investors can invest in the company and receive a newly created cryptocurrency token issued by this company. This token can either represent the service or product the company provides or simply a representation for stake ownership."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"0fd9f6533066","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"cbd758c0f6060","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"ICO Process"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"9f4431123432","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e5cde818dff30","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"In a standardized ICO process, the initiator of the project and the company need to choose one of the structures of ICO. Some of the common structures include:"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"9cb2190c409d","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"9663178ecbd50","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Static Pool:"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"060963ed2f74","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"be5ea4d940ec0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"A predetermined funding goal/limit is set. The total number and price for tokens in the pool are fixed."}],"level":2,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"db67909815d6","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ca2e73a7a6e50","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Dynamic Pool (1.0)"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"a768e38ae555","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"27dc270a07be0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The token price is static, while the total amount of tokens is fixed."}],"level":2,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"075c9f712240","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e8fe76a21c000","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Dynamic Pool (2.0)"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"db285fa7ff6f","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0d8b5e4453ec0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The amount of tokens is static, while the token price is fixed."}],"level":2,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"745a265bd72b","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"8cc95a1d9ca2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"483a11722225","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-b4a36b718603043357252129fe71143f8c3fdd9b-660x417-png","_type":"reference"}},{"_key":"c93abb56c6ff","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f222f8c7e9b00","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Regulation"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"c6f6a158f544","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"aaa188aa03d40","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"A key feature to note about ICO is that "},{"_key":"aaa188aa03d41","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"anyone can launch an ICO."},{"_key":"aaa188aa03d42","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" There are few regulations around the process of ICO, in contrast to the sophisticated and highly standardized IPO process (which is supervised by centralized authorities)."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"1eb23729a53f","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"4c664ed126640","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The lack of regulation lowers the barrier to funding and exposes more businesses to possible funds. However, the lack of regulation also increases the possibility of fraud and scams. "},{"_key":"1f98c81cefcc","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Therefore, it is especially crucial for investors who are interested in ICO to do sufficient research before investing in a type of crypto asset so that the probability of investing in a scam business can be minimized."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"d58cf7f993b3","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"83551d591e96","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"63aa8c5663fe","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-27e364299dd315244b99b6dc3a33f57c436b3146-800x443-png","_type":"reference"}},{"_key":"4cc0b6a949ef","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"214df488dba50","_type":"span","marks":["em"],"text":"Image source: "},{"_key":"214df488dba51","_type":"span","marks":["52aaab1585a3","em"],"text":"https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/initial-coin-offering-ico-letters-technology-concept-business-finance-economy-low-poly-design-style-currency-crypto-banking-online-203202594.jpg"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"52aaab1585a3","_type":"link","href":"https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/initial-coin-offering-ico-letters-technology-concept-business-finance-economy-low-poly-design-style-currency-crypto-banking-online-203202594.jpg"}],"style":"normal"}],"comments":[],"description":"IPO in De-Fi world.","mainImage":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-3289313ce046e1cafef6bacd311407acaf7c6f3a-2083x1080-jpg","_type":"reference"}},"slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"initial-coin-offering-ico"},"title":"Initial Coin Offering (ICO)"}},"__N_SSG":true}